<span class="header1">Arts/Communications paired with Business/Management (BC)</span>

<p>A "BC" pairing indicates that you are a "fun" person. You are able to work with many different types of people and, more than likely, they enjoy working with you. One of your assets is your ability to appreciate others for who they are and what they add to a project. You also can work on several tasks at one time. You don't need much direction on how to complete a task or assignment because you combine creativity with the ability to get things done. You are likely to be very dedicated to your work.</p>
<p>Most occupations in this pairing require at least a Bachelor's Degree. Some require post high school courses.</p>

